Add a column to a gt

Source: R/gt_extensions.R
gt_add_column.Rd

Add a column to a gt

Usage

gt_add_column(tab, .col, .val, ...)

Arguments

tab

A gt table with class gt_tbl

.col

column name

.val

value to add

...

additional arguments to pass to dplyr::add_row

Value

A gt::gt

Examples

rict(wv) |> gt_add_column(r, 3)
